I have evidence of the crime right here.

00:02:42.240 --> 00:02:43.300
Who is this person?

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:44.400
I don't know.

00:02:49.870 --> 00:02:51.750
The Eldest Prince ordered a massacre
at Xiaohe Village last night,

00:02:51.750 --> 00:02:52.910
leaving no survivors,

00:02:52.910 --> 00:02:54.680
so that auspicious clouds
would appear in the sky

00:02:54.680 --> 00:02:56.150
on the day of the ceremony.

00:02:57.470 --> 00:02:59.530
But those were no auspicious clouds.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:02.590
That was the fire
from the destroyed Xiaohe Village.

00:03:02.590 --> 00:03:04.000
This... this isn't true.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:04.750
Father,

00:03:04.910 --> 00:03:06.430
I never did any of these things!

00:03:06.430 --> 00:03:09.560
These are the confessions of your men
after they were captured.

00:03:09.560 --> 00:03:12.000
What was destroyed today
was just an empty village.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:12.870
The villagers of Xiaohe Village

00:03:12.870 --> 00:03:14.730
were evacuated by us beforehand.

00:03:15.030 --> 00:03:16.750
Your men have confessed

00:03:16.750 --> 00:03:18.150
to all your evil deeds.

00:03:19.190 --> 00:03:20.850
Take a good look for yourself.

00:03:20.960 --> 00:03:22.560
Who exactly deserves to die?

00:03:23.750 --> 00:03:24.560
Well...

00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:27.430
Who are you?

00:03:27.680 --> 00:03:29.800
How dare you enter the palace uninvited?

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:30.310
Guards!

00:03:30.310 --> 00:03:31.079
Father!

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:34.220
He called His Majesty Father.

00:03:34.280 --> 00:03:35.000
This...

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:36.030
He's also a prince.

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:36.910
Could it be...

00:03:37.190 --> 00:03:38.400
He's a prince?

00:03:39.680 --> 00:03:41.240
Father, please calm your anger.

00:03:41.240 --> 00:03:42.440
It's been a long time.

00:03:42.750 --> 00:03:43.630
Have you forgotten

00:03:43.630 --> 00:03:45.430
that you still have a son like me?

00:03:53.079 --> 00:03:54.590
It's you.

00:03:55.430 --> 00:03:56.280
Jun Che?

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:00.800
Weren't you dead?

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:03.910
I did die once,

00:04:04.030 --> 00:04:05.840
all thanks to you.

00:04:06.280 --> 00:04:08.360
Now I've crawled back from hell

00:04:09.240 --> 00:04:10.950
to claim your life.

00:04:13.680 --> 00:04:14.480
Jun Che,

00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:16.920
I'm glad that you're back.

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.829
Don't be foolish.

00:04:19.630 --> 00:04:21.870
Let's wait until
everything is investigated.

00:04:21.870 --> 00:04:23.680
The evidence is irrefutable.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:25.270
What's there to investigate?

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:26.510
You just want to cover it up,

00:04:26.510 --> 00:04:28.070
to save the royal family's face

00:04:28.070 --> 00:04:30.190
and bury the Eldest Prince's
heinous crimes

00:04:30.190 --> 00:04:31.430
in darkness,

00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:33.800
keeping everyone in the dark.

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.190
This son you favor so much—

00:04:36.870 --> 00:04:39.330
you think he's
a capable and virtuous ruler,

00:04:39.390 --> 00:04:40.630
but in fact,

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:42.750
he's nothing but a complete fool,

00:04:42.800 --> 00:04:44.480
a worthless coward
without virtue or ability.

00:04:44.480 --> 00:04:45.120
You!

00:04:46.830 --> 00:04:48.120
I didn't come today

00:04:48.510 --> 00:04:50.870
to discuss our father-son relationship.

00:04:50.870 --> 00:04:52.360
I'm here to tear away

00:04:52.360 --> 00:04:54.120
this hypocritical royal facade

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:55.920
and expose all the darkness within

00:04:55.920 --> 00:04:58.270
to the light of day.

00:05:00.480 --> 00:05:01.310
Let me see.

00:05:01.600 --> 00:05:02.390
What is she doing?

00:05:02.390 --> 00:05:03.720
What is this?

00:05:04.420 --> 00:05:05.040
[Lin's Clinic]

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.040
Let me take a look.

00:05:08.510 --> 00:05:10.480
Now throughout the entire Daning City,

00:05:10.480 --> 00:05:12.630
