00:05:12.630 --> 00:05:14.190
The crimes committed by the Eldest Prince

00:05:14.190 --> 00:05:16.040
are already known to all.

00:05:16.920 --> 00:05:18.180
How could you possibly

00:05:18.430 --> 00:05:19.960
produce so many manifestos

00:05:20.600 --> 00:05:21.870
in one single night?

00:05:23.430 --> 00:05:25.190
