to bring peace to the state,

00:05:34.159 --> 00:05:36.720
but why are your writings now
filled with nothing but flattery?

00:05:36.720 --> 00:05:37.510
Tonight,

00:05:37.680 --> 00:05:39.830
I'd like to ask you all
to pick up your brushes again,

00:05:39.830 --> 00:05:41.890
to write not praises but manifestos,

00:05:42.190 --> 00:05:44.800
